AUTHOR: 64Corex
CREDITS: 64Corex

_____________________________________


Extract bunker_v1.bsp to:


cstrike/maps

Located by default:

C:/Program Files/Steam/steamapps/username/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps

_____________________________________

Map description:

Small map, good for quick games. Hardcore deathmatch lovers might love this map.


Features:

- Simple.

- Low space required on disk hard drive.

- Low in texture space.

- No lag / Lag free.

_____________________________________

Enjoy the map

For any bugs, you can contact me:

sergeantmacarthur@gmail.com


Also, you can comment or pm me in FPSBanana, if you leave me a pm please tell me the name of the map and the bug.


NOTE:

This is my first map, I wanted to start with a simple and small map, please give me feedbacks on how I could make it even better.

Thanks to everyone.
